long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Save the time spent in filling applications for accelerators, grants, etc... 

Signup and create a Dantia account first. Then, fill the form in our Dantia web application and we will autocomplete all the others for you!

With this extension you will be able to complete forms in seconds. You just need to review it! When necessary, we use AI models to generate the answers for you, but no worries, your data remains protected inside our application and it's not shared with any third party.

Hope you'll enjoy Dantia Auto-filling!

The Dantia Team
